defaultEEF, the manufacturers’ organisation is the representative voice of UK manufacturing, with offices in London, Brussels, every English region and 
defaultWales. We are a not for profit organisation with a growing membership of almost 6,000 companies of all sizes, employing some 900,000 people from every sector of the engineering, manufacturing and technology based industries. UK Steel, a division of EEF, is
default the trade association for the UK steel industry.  It represents all the country’s steelmakers and a large number of downstream steel processers.
