defaultEEF 
defaultwelcomes the opportunity to provide our views on the Commons Select Committee’s Call for Evidence on Low Carbon Innovation.  EEF has long argued that a strong culture of innovation holds the key to overcoming technological challenges, minimising the cost o
defaultf meeting future climate change targets and in capitalising on the economic 
defaultopportunities
default from green growth.
